Get selectivity process error log likelihoods (positive)

Get_sel_PE_loglik.Rd

Get selectivity process error log likelihoods (positive)

Usage

Get_sel_PE_loglik(PE_model, PE_pars, ln_devs, map_sel_devs, sel_vals)

Arguments

PE_model

Process error model values (1, 2, 3, 4, and 5) (iid, random walk, 3d marginal, 3d conditional, and 2dar1)

PE_pars

Process error parameters

ln_devs

Deviations

map_sel_devs

selectivity deviations to share

sel_vals

Selectivity values

Value

numeric value of log likelihood (in positive space)
